## Installation of Vagrant through CLI Mode:
## Before Vagrant install Virtual Box must be install to run any VM images of OS in virtualbox

    install vagrant

## Configure of vagrant in Local machine
    mkdir vagrant
    cd vagrant
  
##Add default vagrant box 

    vagrant box add hashicorp/precise32
  
##Add configuration to Vagrantfile

    vim Vagrantfile

##Set precise32 as default box. Set port forwarding from 5000 (localhost:5000) to 80 on the guest machine (vargant).

  > Vagrant.configure("2") do |config|
    config.vm.box = "hashicorp/precise32"
    config.vm.network "forwarded_port", host: 5000, guest: 80
  end
  
##Start vagrant machine

    vagrant up

##Check vargant status
  
    vagrant status
  
##Reload vargant configuration

    vagrant reload
  
##Stop vagrant

    vagrant halt
  
##Login to vagrant machine

     vagrant ssh

## Unstall Vagrant
    rm -rf /opt/vagrant
    rm -f /usr/bin/vagrant